$J2|p_{ij}=1;r_j|\sum U_j$ is NP-hard \\
$J2|p_{ij}=1|\sum w_jU_j$ is NP-hard \\
$O|p_{ij}=1;r_j|\sum U_j$ is NP-hard \\
$O|p{ij}=1|\sum w_jU_j$ is fixed parameter tractable \\}
}

